{"title":"“全民国家”怪现状","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“全民国家”怪现状"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在勃列日涅夫集团反动统治下的苏联，犯罪现象日益严重，社会弊病丛生。苏修当局一再实行“加强法制”，也无济于事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“全民国家”顶呱呱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犯罪兴旺又发达。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大官小官贪污成风气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党阀党棍受贿算合法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂厂长搞投机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农庄主席惯倒把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酗酒寻常事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流氓满街耍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年吸毒品，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿飞打群架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑市交易到处有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妓女出没华灯下……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫斯科城赶纽约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁格勒赛罗马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警察频添增，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"监狱屡扩大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刑罚再加码，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克格勃喽罗忙乱煞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统统是白搭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君不见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窃钩小偷坐班房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窃国大盗笑哈哈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌拉，勃氏王朝的“太平天下”！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}